{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An ancient, terrible power lies waiting\u2026</h2>Max has always been the more unhinged member of the Freelance Police\u2014a lovable lunatic with a knack for spreading chaos wherever he goes. But recently his abilities have taken a supernatural turn.<br><br>It all started when he stumbled upon a mysterious toy that allows him to glimpse the future. Now Sam &amp; Max have aroused the attention of a host of villains from across the galaxy who are hellbent on acquiring the magical Toys of Power to achieve their own ends.<br><br>As those who seek the Devil\u2019s Toybox close in and Max\u2019s psychic abilities grow beyond his control, the Freelance Police will come up against their most frightening adversary yet: the power of Max\u2019s mind.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648050/extras/devilsplayhouse-street-teaser-600px.jpg?t=1728164417\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>A bizarre paranormal adventure:</strong> Explore odd locales, meet eccentric characters, and solve brain-tickling puzzles in an interactive story with a surprise around every corner.<br></li><li> <strong>Rabbity-thing mind meld:</strong> Jump into Max\u2019s brain and use the Toys of Power to see the future, teleport, read minds, and other tricks.<br></li><li> <strong>No walkthrough required:</strong> The game detects when you\u2019re stuck and provides subtle hints.<br></li><li> <strong>Beautifully remastered:</strong> Lighting, lip-sync, cinematography, music, and more have been updated and enhanced to bring Telltale\u2019s 2010 episodic season up to modern standards.<br></li><li> <strong>Last in a trilogy:</strong> See the episodic Sam &amp; Max series through to its epic conclusion.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Soothsayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2648050/7bf09d9c387cd0fc3b32bb